description: This file defines a React functional component named 'Square' used as a UI element in a Tic-Tac-Toe game. It renders a button representing a game board square, showing its value ('X', 'O', or empty), and handles user interactions such as clicking, with support for visual highlighting and accessibility features.

methods.name: Square
methods.description: React functional component that renders an interactive button representing a game square with various visual states and accessibility features.
